Package grafioschtrader.connector.instrument.investing

Class InvestingConnector

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.connector.instrument.BaseFeedConnector
grafioschtrader.connector.instrument.investing.InvestingConnector
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFeedConnector
@Component public class InvestingConnector extends BaseFeedConnector
Historical data could also be downloaded from Investing.com. Since 2022-10-18 this no longer works, as access is secured via Cloudflare. However, the methods for historical data are still available in the source code. There is both a regex pattern check and a connector check for the URL extension of the corresponding instrument.
